  <brief_title>Trial of Weight Bearing Status Following Femoral Revision With Tapered, Fluted, Titanium Stems</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial of Weight Bearing Status Following Femoral Revision With Tapered, Fluted, Titanium Stems</official_title>
