  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, randomized controlled trial of all patients undergoing femoral&#xD;
      revision at Thomas Jefferson University Hospital and Rothman Institute undergoing femoral&#xD;
      revision surgery with the use of a modern titanium, fluted, tapered stem. At the time of&#xD;
      surgery, patients will be randomized to six weeks of toe-touch weight bearing or immediate&#xD;
      weight bearing as tolerated&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
